166
00:08:23,170 --> 00:08:25,160
You're not happy I'm getting a divorce?

167
00:08:25,870 --> 00:08:28,700
Fine, I am. Boy...

168
00:08:28,710 --> 00:08:30,800
I got a divorce, but it's not good.

169
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:33,690
