199
00:10:33,370 --> 00:10:35,890
So watch out and don't slip.

200
00:10:35,900 --> 00:10:38,240
You must be busy. I'm hanging up.

201
00:10:39,850 --> 00:10:41,240
Okay.

202
00:10:42,250 --> 00:10:43,890
Goodbye, mother.

203
00:10:47,900 --> 00:10:50,100
So, will you move...

204
00:10:54,500 --> 00:10:56,340
I will.

205
00:10:56,350 --> 00:10:57,570
Yeongdal!

206
00:11:01,670 --> 00:11:02,990
I need to ask you something.

207
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:05,030
I dropped by on my way to a shop.

208
00:11:05,040 --> 00:11:07,190
Did my uncle call?

209
00:11:09,400 --> 00:11:11,030
