210
00:11:13,040 --> 00:11:14,690
Oh, man.

211
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:19,360
Yeongdal, let me ask you one thing.

212
00:11:19,370 --> 00:11:22,600
Do you love my uncle?

213
00:11:25,400 --> 00:11:27,630
